Text: Crazy! Nearly another 100 completed. Many thanks for all your hard work Biomechanical.

As always, another great job.
Appreciated.

Biomechanical: I really appreciate all your work in uploading these. You are making a difference!

I've been exposed to soooo many new bands and songs, I love it. Really breaks up my day in the office to put on a few new albums and ROCK OUT while my co-workers drone on to each other about their lives...
